{"tid":2148770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【地產專題】名牌撤走 中環地舖淪鞋店散貨場","createTime":"2020-08-10T05:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T05:47:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5ebd2a8e871dd5741ac2bbd593b3879ea15389a5","tid":2148770,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200810/7V4FFVNUMZBE5GWWRGGUDU3II4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200810%2F7V4FFVNUMZBE5GWWRGGUDU3II4%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=1bf7c72c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200810%2F7V4FFVNUMZBE5GWWRGGUDU3II4%2F&h=52bfea73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200810/7V4FFVNUMZBE5GWWRGGUDU3II4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【地產專題】名牌撤走 中環地舖淪鞋店散貨場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政治及金融重心的中環區，過往吸引國際品牌爭相在區內開業，但肺炎疫情影響、經濟急速逆轉，零售市道疲弱，昔日高檔品牌搶租情景不復見。相反區內甲級商廈地舖，面積近3,800方呎，卻淪為美國中檔鞋履品牌Skechers散貨場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tqBhrXDni88t_NNnSxVOPM7OaG0=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6XOIBSVUGZGRZMEZT3EUO2QXIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtqBhrXDni88t_NNnSxVOPM7OaG0%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6XOIBSVUGZGRZMEZT3EUO2QXIQ.jpg&h=d4cbfb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Skechers中環特賣場無「揼本」裝潢，貨品只用鞋盒堆砌在不同貨架。<br />\n<br />\n中環昔日有西班牙連鎖店ZARA以過千萬元搶租瑞典品牌H&amp;M舖位，亦有以美國服裝品牌A&amp;F以天價700萬元承租畢打行地庫，然而統統已成過去；即便最新的娛樂行地舖韓國名牌MCM亦宣告撤出中環，改由法國運動用品迪卡儂（DECATHLON）頂上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kxhtBU4ZiblDSpYdVI7i5-Am_3M=/709x403/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QPVNDN3E3JABLKIMUGCX65PEHU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkxhtBU4ZiblDSpYdVI7i5-Am_3M%3D%2F709x403%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQPVNDN3E3JABLKIMUGCX65PEHU.gif&h=d0a1df2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區內吉舖湧現 減價三成招租<br />\n<br />\n曾為攝影器材界龍頭的廣大攝影，其第三代家族成員鍾國鎏早年以1.2億元購入皇后大道中152號商廈並重建，商廈落成卻「生不逢時」，該廈地舖面積達3,784方呎，並鄰近中環中。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n周大福2015年租用同一地段39號地舖作特賣場，該店主要銷售細價鑽飾、K金。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n隨着國際名店搶租不再，區內吉舖漸現，其中皇后大道中110至116。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，領展（823）將商戶。。。。。。。。"}]}